AUTHORS
--------------------------------------------------

The primary developers are David W. Caress of the Monterey Bay Aquarium 
Research Institute and Dale N. Chayes of the Lamont-Doherty Earth 
Observatory (L-DEO) of Columbia University. 

Val Schmidt, an engineer at L-DEO, joined the MB-System team during 2002. 
Val, now a graduate student at the Center for Coastal and Ocean Mapping at 
the University of New Hampshire, has worked to develop polished 
MB-System documentation, particularly the MB-System Cookbook.

